Pre-Game Insights: Cyprus rounded off a dismal qualifying campaign with a loss to Spain.
Lithuania fared better in their qualifying campaign but struggled on the road.
Cyprus' only recent win came against Greece in the Nations League.
Lithuania secured a crucial point against Montenegro but faced challenges in qualifying.
Cyprus and Lithuania are both aiming to avoid relegation to League D.
Ketsbaia may experiment with his Cyprus team, while Lithuania has key absences.
